sourceInformation: Ancestry.com. Texas, U.S., Birth Certificates, 1903-1932 [database on-line]. Provo, UT, USA: Ancestry.com Operations, Inc., 2013. Original data: Texas Department of State Health Services. Texas Birth Certificates, 1903–1932. iArchives, Orem, Utah.
sourceDescription: This database contains birth certificates from the Texas Department of State Health Services, for the years 1903–1932. Some amendments to certificates of birth are included as well. Learn more...
